<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الباب الحادي والستون فيما قيل في اللّين والشدَّة والمجازاة<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٥٢٥)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">لبعضهم:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١ - وَكَالسَّيْفِ إِنْ لا يَنْتَهُ لانَ مَسُّهُ ... وَحَدَّاهُ إِنْ خَاشَنْتَهُ خَشِنَانُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٥٢٦)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ عَنْتَرَةُ بنُ شَدَّادٍ العَبْسِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الكامل)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١ - أَثْنِي عَلَيَّ بمَا عَلِمْتِ فَإنَّنِي ... سَمْحٌ مُخَالَقَتِي إِذَا لَمْ أُظْلَمِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٢ - فَإِذَا ظُلِمْتُ فإِنَّ ظُلْمِيَ بَاسِلٌ ... مُرٌّ مَذَاقَتُهُ كَطَعْمِ الْعَلْقَمِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٥٢٧)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ آخَرُ:</span> <span class="c2">(البسيط)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>١ - حُلْوٌ مُلايَنَتِي شِكْسٌ مُثَاوَرَتِي ... عَفٌّ عَلانِيَتِي لا أَعْرِفُ الْخَمَرَا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٥٢٨)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ لَبِيدُ بنُ رَبِيعَةَ الَعَامِرِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(المنسرح)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>١ - حُلْوٌ كَرِيمٌ وَفِي حَلاوَتِهِ ... مُرٌّ لَطِيفُ الأَحْشَاءِ وَالْكَبِدِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>